hesitates
or loses power while driving
the transmission slips or jerks
the check engine light is illuminated
the vehicle is unable to accelerate
the RPM revs up or down.

the vehicle hesitates or loses power while driving

the vehicle is unable to accelerate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The loss of power or acceleration can cause the vehicle to stall or hesitate while driving, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Airbag Malfunction and Failure to Deploy
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to serious injury or death in the event of an accident, as the airbags may not deploy properly or at all.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the airbag deploys unexpectedly
the airbag does not deploy in the event of an accident
the horn does not work
the cruise control and lights malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the horn can lead to accidents or near-misses, as the driver may not be able to alert other drivers or pedestrians of their presence.
symptoms: The horn does not work
the airbag warning light is illuminated
the cruise control and lights malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure to properly repair recalled vehicles can lead to ongoing safety issues, including airbag malfunction and failure to deploy.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is still illuminated after recall repair
the airbag deploys unexpectedly
the airbag does not deploy in the event of an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to shut down, resulting in loss of power, loss of brakes, and other safety-critical systems, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle shuts down

the check engine warning light illuminates
the vehicle jerks or hesitates
